=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223795023\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221590994100\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy pdf is not? \u0022Portable Document Format\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EBoth acronyms and initialisms are made up of the first letter or letters of the words in a phrase. The word\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eacronym\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Etypically applies when the resulting thing can be read as a word; for example,\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eradar\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ecomes from \u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Era\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Edio\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ed\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eetection\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ea\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003End\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Er\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eanging\u0022 and\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Escuba\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ecomes from \u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Es\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eelf-\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ec\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eontained\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eu\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Enderwater\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eb\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ereathing\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ea\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Epparatus.\u0022 The word\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Einitialism\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eonly applies when the resulting thing is read as an abbreviation; for example\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EDIY\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E, which comes from \u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ed\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eo\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ei\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Et\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Ey\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eourself,\u0022 is pronounced by saying the names of the letters. Note that the word\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eacronym\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eis also sometimes used to mean \u0022initialism.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-01T10:30:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223795076\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591006988\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EThe word\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eacronym\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f8f8f8;color:#4d5156;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Etypically applies when the resulting thing can be read as a word\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I can read it: /pdf!/\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-01T10:38:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223795080\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591007420\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I can read it: /pdf!/\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut you\u0027re just pronouncing\u00A0the letters, pee-dee-eff, instead of pronouncing it as a word, like Nasa, radar, laser, lidar, scuba, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-01T10:41:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223795081\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591007919\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut you\u0027re just pronouncing\u00A0the letters, pee-dee-eff, instead of pronouncing it as a word, like Nasa, radar, laser, lidar, scuba, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\